{
  "stem": "13655.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 320.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They're crying.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It's hard to describe.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "No pen can [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "All of a sudden, you're staying.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they're coming more, and more, and more, and you're surrounded from Germans.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "All kind of Gestapo. sonderkommando, the Luftwaffe, and Polish police, [INAUDIBLE], [?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Ukrainians, ?] you name it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Finally, the daylight comes up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Everybody privately was thinking, maybe it's going to come a hand to stop [? that. ?] So what happened?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I finally, in the [INAUDIBLE], I [? found ?] my two brothers.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's very hard.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was very hard to find each other.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The beating, the knocking was-- we didn't know, like wolves.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All of them, what I said, just.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "SS, the Wehrmacht, and the Gestapo--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They're beating the people, and knocking, and the whole road, maybe about 10 blocks, was already people killed and laying and calling to shoot me, finish me.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Finally, what happened?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They took-- the day is there, and [INAUDIBLE],.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Right away, they took people in the side, should dig holes for themselves.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Me and my two brothers, they took to the Luftwaffe, to the airport.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Outskirts from Biala.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Some of them, they took away in another place.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I didn't know it well.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We didn't know one from the other what's going on.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They took us there, and I didn't know what happened to the wife, the sister, the children, and so forth.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I go into the airport.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Another Polish [NON-ENGLISH] came in to that direction.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We didn't know what.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They pushed us in to the airport in barracks, and they took us out to work for half a day.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The work was very bad, heavy labor work.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I see my brother got beaten up already, my older brother.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then, at night, they took us into the barracks.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No food, no life.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
